TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Lookup to get the ITEM_ID and BUSINESS_SEG_HIERARCHY_ID.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_SLBA_ITEM

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT MAX(ITEM.ITEM_ID) as ITEM_ID, MAX(ITEM.BUSINESS_SEG_HIERARCHY_ID) as BUSINESS_SEG_HIERARCHY_ID, TRIM(ITEM.SKU) as SKU, TRIM(ITEM.STYLE_NUM) as STYLE_NUM, TRIM(ITEM.COLOR_CODE) as COLOR_CODE, TRIM(ITEM.SIZE_CODE) as SIZE_CODE FROM ( select distinct bsh.business_seg_hierarchy_id, i.item_id, i.style_num, i.color_code, i.sku, i.size_code from slba.item i JOIN style_master_1 sm ON i.style_num = sm.style_num and i.division_group = sm.division_group and nvl(trim(i.company_code), '--') = sm.company_code JOIN fcst_business_seg_hierarchy bsh ON sm.sbu_desc = bsh.strategic_business_unit_desc ) ITEM GROUP BY ITEM.SKU, ITEM.STYLE_NUM, ITEM.COLOR_CODE, ITEM.SIZE_CODE

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SKU = I_SKU AND STYLE_NUM = I_STYLE_NUM AND COLOR_CODE = I_COLOR_CODE AND SIZE_CODE = I_SIZE_CODE

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: To filter the records which are shipment date is having less than todays date.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: FL_SHIP_DATE

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Filter Condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
IN(ltrim(rtrim(DESCRIPTION)) , 'Confirmed','PO Received','Commit')
AND SHIP_DATE>= MIN_DAY_DATE
AND (NOT ISNULL(LTRIM(RTRIM(PRODUCT_CODE))) AND LENGTH(LTRIM(RTRIM(PRODUCT_CODE)))!=0)
AND LENGTH(LTRIM(RTRIM(CUSTOMER))) <> 0

ATTRIBUTE.NAME: Pre SQL
Post SQL
ATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
UPDATE INFO_ETL_CNTL_TBL SET TGT_VAL=( SELECT count(*) FROM FCST_FUTURE_EVENTS WHERE UPDATE_TIMESTAMP= (SELECT MAX(MAP_RUN_DT) FROM INFO_ETL_CNTL_TBL WHERE INFO_MAP_NAME = 'm_TR020C_FCST_FUTR_EVE' AND MAP_RUN_DT <=SYSDATE)) WHERE INFO_MAP_NAME = 'm_TR020C_FCST_FUTR_EVE' AND MAP_RUN_DT=(SELECT MAX(MAP_RUN_DT) FROM INFO_ETL_CNTL_TBL WHERE INFO_MAP_NAME = 'm_TR020C_FCST_FUTR_EVE' AND MAP_RUN_DT <=SYSDATE ) ;
UPDATE INFO_ETL_CNTL_TBL SET STATUS_YN = (CASE WHEN SRC_VAL = TGT_VAL THEN 'Y' ELSE 'N' END ) WHERE INFO_MAP_NAME = 'm_TR020C_FCST_FUTR_EVE' AND MAP_RUN_DT=(SELECT MAX(MAP_RUN_DT) FROM INFO_ETL_CNTL_TBL WHERE INFO_MAP_NAME = 'm_TR020C_FCST_FUTR_EVE' AND MAP_RUN_DT <=SYSDATE );
